text: Nagel can refer to: * Nagel (surname), a surname and people with that surname * Nagel, Bavaria, a town in the district of Wunsiedel, Bavaria, Germany * Naglfar, a boat made of nails from the dead in Germanic mythology * Nagel point, a geometric center of a triangle * Thomas Nagel, philosopher * Ernest Nagel, philosopher (1901 – 1985) es:Clavo ja:ネイル yi:נאגל
